OL,3,CManufacturing ends at Denby Pottery as
OL,4,Cno buyer found
OL,6,FAll manufacturing is to stop at
OL,7,Fpottery firm Denby and a further 49
OL,8,Fworkers have been made redundant.
OL,10,FAdministrators were appointed at the
OL,11,Fend of March, who started a process to
OL,12,Ftry to find a buyer for the business.
OL,14,FTony Wright, joint administrator of
OL,15,Fthe Denby Group and partner at FRP,
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is another very difficult
OL,17,Fday for the skilled workers at Denby
OL,18,Fand we understand how devastating this
OL,19,Fnews will be for those affected and
OL,20,Ftheir families.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
