OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776942175
OL,3,CManufacturing ends at Denby Pottery as
OL,4,Cno buyer found
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, despite extensive
OL,7,Fefforts, we have been unable to find a
OL,8,Fbuyer for the manufacturing operations
OL,9,Fand have had to take this difficult
OL,10,Fdecision.
OL,12,F"We remain in discussions with
OL,13,Finterested parties regarding other
OL,14,Fparts of the business and continue to
OL,15,Fdo everything we can to support
OL,16,Faffected employees through this
OL,17,Fprocess."
