OL,3,CManufacturing ends at Denby Pottery as
OL,4,Cno buyer found
OL,6,FDenby Pottery was established in 1809
OL,7,Fnear Ripley in Derbyshire. The company
OL,8,Fannounced on Tuesday 31 March that it
OL,9,Fhad gone into formal administration.
OL,11,FAfter 217 years, the firm said it had
OL,12,Fentered "challenging times" and
OL,13,F"enormous financial challenges" with
OL,14,Freduced spending from customers,
OL,15,Fhigher employment costs and surging
OL,16,Fenergy prices.
